(10, 'aKVAOMwzC2Q', 'Ispat Indo dan Indonesia, Memiliki Kesan Tersendiri di Hati Keluarga Mittal', 'DendiRiki', '<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Kali ini Ispat Indo kedatangan 2 Petinggi Ispat Indo Holding Corporation,</p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Part 1 : Mrs. Parul Jain, (Vice President Mittal Family Investment, Head M&amp;A and Corporate Finance, serta Head<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; </span>&amp; Lead seluruh investasi ekuitas/ekuitas swasta strategis di perusahaan)<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; min-height: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Corner Talk kali ini kita akan membahas dalam 10-15 tahun Indonesia akan menjadi negara dengan perekonomian yang akan dibicarakan semua orang.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; min-height: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Simak pembahasan selengkapnya divideo ini dan nantikan pembahasan part 2 dalam corner talk berikutnya.</p>', '2024-07-08 05:16:01', '2024-07-08 05:16:01'),
(11, 'mQiCUFB2cic', 'Analisa dan keyakinan Presdir Ispat Indo pada dunia bisnis di era VUCA dan pemilu.', 'DendiRiki', '<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Di video sebelumnya kita sudah membahas salah satu petinggi Ispat Indo Holding Corporation, di part 2 ini kita akan membahas Mr. Philippe Darmayan, beliau adalah CEO-Distribution Solutions &amp; Executive VP at ArcelorMittal SA Chairman for ArcelorMittal France SAS, Chief Executive Officer at ArcelorMittal Distribution Solutions SA and President for ArcelorMittal Atlantique et Lorraine</p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; min-height: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Temukan strategi dan visi bisnis di tengah tantangan era VUCA dan suasana pemilu melalui pandangan Presiden Direktur Ispat Indo. Dalam video ini, beliau membagikan analisis mendalamnya, memberikan pemahaman yang kaya akan keyakinan dan langkah-langkah strategis yang diambil untuk tetap sukses di tengah dinamika bisnis yang berubah-ubah.</p>', '2024-07-08 05:18:59', '2024-07-08 05:18:59');

